metadata.name: Skulls On Chain #1
metadata.description: Skulls On Chain is a NFT collection of 5555 hand drawn digital art layers stored on chain on the Ethereum Blockchain. All trait layers are digitally hand-drawn and inscribed onto the Ethereum Blockchain. This process ensures that the artwork will not be hosted on a centralized web server, which could potentially result in the artwork becoming unlinked if the server went down. This shift to on chain is a significant step forward for the future of Skulls On-Chain, as well as for many other NFT projects launching on chain, as it safeguards all collectors and investors from losing their artwork. Once the artwork is on chain, it can never be changed or removed, unless the entire Ethereum Blockchain is deleted and wiped clean. A project by 8BW3.
